{
  "stem": "11882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they told a classmate of mine, Ingemouse-- Ingeborg Giese-- who had been born-- born in Germany and come to America as a 12-year-old-- they knew she was going back as an unemployed schoolteacher, just as myself.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was going back to her native Germany, to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they thought, would she please visit their relatives and give them some English instruction?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, sure, she would, and took the addresses and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And went over and gradually brought over, I would say, five or six of us classmates, unemployed teachers-- I mean, we had little jobs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could make $13 a week in a department store or something, but we wanted-- we had all this training and wanted to get teaching jobs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There just was no opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially for Catholic school graduates at that moment in that area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at any rate, she brought us one after the other over to Hamburg, Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we spent a period of time there, several months or so, had teaching experience on our records in a Berlitz, in another language school, teaching English-- to the many people in Germany who wanted to learn English, because they wanted to get out, and because Germans could not travel at that time.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Germany's a big travel company of today-- country of today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Could take only-- unless they had a very good political reason-- could take only 10 marks with them out-- out of the country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, you can't live in England, you can't study in Italy without a little money, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they all came to us as to a foreign country to learn English-- become an English correspondent in some business, or learn English just for the culture of it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were busy, busy, busy.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
